schools.name: Governor Samuel Wilder King Intermediate School

data.description: This fully remodeled single-family home boasts an open floor plan. Situated one house from the ocean, you experience both tropical landscaping throughout the spacious fenced-in yard as well as ocean views from the living room. The 6 car driveway is EV ready w/ a 50A/220V outlet. A large deck & pavers in the front leave plenty of room for entertaining w/ nearby water access for a short paddle to the famous Kaneohe Sandbar. Luxury vinyl flooring & built-in closets. The kitchen includes all stainless appliances, backsplash to the ceiling, & handmade mango wood shelving. Plenty of storage & a wine fridge. In-home laundry & full AC w/ mini-splits in every room. All new windows & doors combined w/ a solar hot water heater & solar attic vent. The BAs consist of new tile, vanities, toilets, & ceiling mounted waterfall shower heads. The seller is providing a home warranty for peace of mind. Home has an assumable 2.25% VA loan at approximately $750,000 to eligible buyers. All comments, data is provided by seller. Buyer to confirm all & hold all parties harmless from any discrepancy data in the mls & advertising. Ltd Service Addendum signed by seller/s must be sign by buyer/s w/ Contract.
